Package org.jboss.windup.reporting.model

Interface InlineHintModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EffortReportModel, com.syncleus.ferma.ElementFrame, FileLocationModel, FileReferenceModel, TaggableModel, ToFileModelTransformable, com.syncleus.ferma.VertexFrame, WindupFrame<org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Vertex>, WindupVertexFrame
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    HardcodedIPLocationModel
    public interface InlineHintModel
extends EffortReportModel, FileLocationModel, TaggableModel
    This is used to classify lines within application source FileModel instances, and to provide hints and related data regarding specific positions within those files.
